---

---

<section id="infos" class="border-t border-neutral-900 bg-black">
  <div
    class="container-narrow py-10 grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.4fr)_minmax(0,1fr)]"
  >
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">
        Informations pratiques.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-300">
        Le studio, salon de tatouage à Chambéry, se situe au cœur de la ville.<br
        />Je travaille uniquement sur rendez-vous, pour des projets préparés
        ensemble en amont à partir de vos envies, références et contraintes.<br
        />
        N'hésitez pas à me contacter pour discuter de votre projet.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
          <div class="space-y-1 min-w-0">
            <p class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-neutral-300">
              Localisation
            </p>
            <a
              href="https://www.google.com/maps?q=4+Rue+Claude+Martin,+73000+Chamb%C3%A9ry"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noreferrer"
              class="text-base font-semibold leading-relaxed hover:text-neutral-50 transition-colors block"
            >
              4 rue Claude Martin<br />
              73000 Chambéry
              <div class="mt-1 text-xs font-normal text-neutral-300">
                Sur rendez-vous uniquement.<br />
                Du mardi au samedi.
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>
          <button
            type="button"
            data-map-open
            class="w-28 h-28 sm:w-32 sm:h-32 rounded-xl border border-neutral-800 bg-neutral-950/60 overflow-hidden shrink-0 cursor-pointer hover:border-neutral-600 transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-neutral-500"
            aria-label="Agrandir le plan"
          >
            <img
              src="/map.png"
              alt="Plan d'accès au studio clm.ink — 4 rue Claude Martin, Chambéry"
              loading="lazy"
              class="h-full w-full object-cover"
            />
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <dl class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 text-sm mt-6">
        <div class="space-y-1 sm:col-span-2">
          <dd class="text-neutral-100">
            <div
              class="rounded-xl border border-neutral-800/70 bg-neutral-900/30 px-4 py-3 flex items-center gap-3"
            >
              <div
                class="inline-flex h-9 w-9 shrink-0 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-full border border-neutral-700 bg-neutral-950/80"
              >
                <img
                  src="/purple_line.jpg"
                  alt="Purple Line tattoo club"
                  loading="lazy"
                  class="h-full w-full object-cover"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="min-w-0">
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-200">
                  clm.ink partage son studio au sein du collectif
                  <a
                    href="https://www.instagram.com/purpleline.tattoo/"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noreferrer"
                    class="whitespace-nowrap underline underline-offset-4 decoration-neutral-400 hover:decoration-neutral-200 text-neutral-100"
                  >
                    Purple Line tattoo club
                  </a>
                  , un salon de tatouage à Chambéry qui réunit six tatoueurs :
                </p>
                <span
                  class="mt-1.5 block flex flex-wrap gap-x-0.5 gap-y-0.5 text-[10px] text-neutral-400"
                >
                  <a
                    href="https://www.instagram.com/suzon_tattoo/"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noreferrer"
                    class="inline-flex items-center rounded px-1 py-0.5 -mx-0.5 -my-0.5 underline underline-offset-2 decoration-neutral-600 hover:decoration-neutral-400 text-neutral-300"
                  >
                    @suzon_tattoo
                  </a>
                  <a
                    href="https://www.instagram.com/m.caligari/"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noreferrer"
                    class="inline-flex items-center rounded px-1 py-0.5 -mx-0.5 -my-0.5 underline underline-offset-2 decoration-neutral-600 hover:decoration-neutral-400 text-neutral-300"
                  >
                    @m.caligari
                  </a>
                  <a
                    href="https://www.instagram.com/bonjour.crapule/"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noreferrer"
                    class="inline-flex items-center rounded px-1 py-0.5 -mx-0.5 -my-0.5 underline underline-offset-2 decoration-neutral-600 hover:decoration-neutral-400 text-neutral-300"
                  >
                    @bonjour.crapule
                  </a>
                  <a
                    href="https://www.instagram.com/cotenoir.ink/"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noreferrer"
                    class="inline-flex items-center rounded px-1 py-0.5 -mx-0.5 -my-0.5 underline underline-offset-2 decoration-neutral-600 hover:decoration-neutral-400 text-neutral-300"
                  >
                    @cotenoir.ink
                  </a>
                  <a
                    href="https://www.instagram.com/clm.ink/"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noreferrer"
                    class="inline-flex items-center rounded px-1 py-0.5 -mx-0.5 -my-0.5 underline underline-offset-2 decoration-neutral-600 hover:decoration-neutral-400 text-neutral-300"
                  >
                    @clm.ink
                  </a>
                  <a
                    href="https://www.instagram.com/primo_kao.tattoo/"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noreferrer"
                    class="inline-flex items-center rounded px-1 py-0.5 -mx-0.5 -my-0.5 underline underline-offset-2 decoration-neutral-600 hover:decoration-neutral-400 text-neutral-300"
                  >
                    @primo_kao.tattoo
                  </a>
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </div>

    <div
      id="contact"
      class="flex flex-col gap-5 rounded-2xl border-2 border-neutral-700 bg-neutral-950/80 p-6 sm:p-8 lg:min-h-0"
    >
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-neutral-400">
          Prise de rendez-vous
        </p>
        <h2
          class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-neutral-50"
        >
          Contactez-moi.
        </h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-300">
        Les réservations se font via Instagram ou par e-mail. Indiquez votre
        projet (zone, style, taille, références) pour avancer ensemble.
      </p>
      <div class="space-y-3 mt-1">
        <a
          href="https://www.instagram.com/clm.ink/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer"
          class="instagram-dm-btn flex items-center justify-between rounded-full border-0 px-4 py-3 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-white shadow-md transition-opacity duration-200 hover:opacity-90"
          style="background: linear-gradient(45deg, #833ab4 0%, #fd1d1d 50%, #f77737 90%, #fcaf45 100%);"
        >
          <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg
              aria-hidden="true"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              class="h-4 w-4 text-white"
            >
              <rect
                x="3"
                y="3"
                width="18"
                height="18"
                rx="5"
                class="fill-none stroke-current"
                stroke-width="1.4"></rect>
              <circle
                cx="12"
                cy="12"
                r="4"
                class="fill-none stroke-current"
                stroke-width="1.4"></circle>
              <circle cx="17.5" cy="6.5" r="1" class="fill-current"></circle>
            </svg>
            <span>DM Instagram</span>
          </span>
        </a>
        <a
          href="mailto:hello@clm-ink.fr?subject=Projet%20tatouage%20-%20clm.ink"
          class="flex items-center justify-between rounded-full border-2 border-neutral-700 bg-neutral-900/50 px-4 py-3 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-neutral-200 hover:border-neutral-100 hover:text-neutral-50 transition-colors"
        >
          <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="h-4 w-4">
              <rect
                x="3"
                y="5"
                width="18"
                height="14"
                rx="2"
                class="fill-none stroke-current"
                stroke-width="1.4"></rect>
              <path
                d="m5 7 7 5 7-5"
                class="fill-none stroke-current"
                stroke-width="1.4"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Email</span>
          </span>
          <span class="text-[10px] text-neutral-400">hello@clm-ink.fr</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-narrow pt-3 pb-6 mb-4" aria-label="Rappels importants">
    <p class="text-[11px] text-neutral-500 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-2">
      Rappels importants
    </p>
    <ul class="text-[11px] text-neutral-600 space-y-0.5 list-none">
      <li>Un acompte pourra vous être demandé pour bloquer une date.</li>
      <li>
        Les mineurs doivent être accompagnés d&apos;un représentant légal, avec
        pièces d&apos;identité.
      </li>
      <li>
        <a
          href="/studio-hygiene"
          class="underline underline-offset-4 decoration-neutral-500 hover:decoration-neutral-400 text-neutral-400"
          >Hygiène et sécurité</a
        > : matériel à usage unique et protocoles stricts.
      </li>
      <li>
        Un tatouage reste un acte définitif. N&apos;hésitez pas à poser toutes
        vos questions avant de vous engager.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<div
  id="map-modal"
  class="fixed inset-0 z-50 hidden items-center justify-center bg-black/90 p-4"
  aria-modal="true"
  aria-label="Plan agrandi"
>
  <button
    type="button"
    data-map-close
    class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full cursor-default"
    aria-label="Fermer le plan"></button>
  <div
    class="relative max-w-4xl w-full max-h-[90vh] flex flex-col items-center"
  >
    <div class="relative w-max max-w-full max-h-[90vh]">
      <button
        type="button"
        data-map-close
        class="absolute top-2 right-2 z-10 inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-neutral-600 text-neutral-200 hover:border-neutral-400 hover:text-neutral-50 bg-black/60"
        aria-label="Fermer"
      >
        ✕
      </button>
      <img
        src="/map_big.png"
        alt="Plan d'accès au studio clm.ink — 4 rue Claude Martin, Chambéry"
        class="max-h-[90vh] max-w-full w-auto h-auto object-contain rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
